{% block main %}
  <div class="container p-4 text-light">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      <a href="https://github.com/chesslablab" target="_blank" class="link-light link-underline-opacity-0 fw-bold">ChesslaBlab</a> is an open-source organization on GitHub creating decentralized chess software.
    </p>
    <hr class="hr">
    <h3>Manifesto</h3>
    <p>We believe:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Chess is a sport, a science, and an art.</li>
      <li>Anyone, regardless of age, race, gender or social background should have access to easy-to-use, decentralized chess platforms and be free to pick which one they choose for their learning.</li>
      <li>Players should have more control over their own online playing.</li>
      <li>Anyone can learn to think more scientifically.</li>
      <li>Anyone can improve their cognitive abilities which is a good think.</li>
      <li>It is a human right to be allowed to develop a thinking mindset.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      These goals can be achieved with open-source software. ChesslaBlab stands for chess laboratory and its repositories can be used and extended to create amazing chess web apps.
    </p>
    <p>
      Happy coding!
    </p>
